{"id":"0f6f6cca-ab4d-4b32-a397-53cce411d235","name":"Elijah Crawford || Old Flame","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Taking all of me,<br>we've already done it in my head</em><br><br><strong>In the wake of a nasty break up, you're face to face with the one who got away.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br>You gave him your best years.<br><br>Six years with your ex and you walk in on him cheating--<br><br>on your anniversary no less!<br><br>Worse?<br><br>He'd tried to accuse you for weeks now that you were flirting too much with you friend and former crush Elijah Crawford. <br><br>You might have fantasized about Elijah but he can't hold your thoughts against you!<br><br>Fuck it.<br><br>You're better off without him. <br><br>And perhaps--<br><br>Better <em>with</em> Elijah?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/UBiBBU-Lq0Jj8mFUMTB07.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/EXpTzFmxBTnj8TiZJQeVS.webp\" style=\"width: 291px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/v_DebF6-WikbA5FZ7f5jP.webp\" style=\"width: 253px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>I'm on vacation!</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">You asked and you shall receive, here is Eli's solo bot!</span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">If you're like moonie, what do you mean Solo bot? You can find Drew and Eli </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/718ba36c-7331-46c2-982e-d885ad925021_character-drew-eli-guilty-as-sin\" target=\"_blank\"><em>here!</em></a><br><br>Drew is not your ex here (unless you want him to be!) but I did use a bad anniversary as a catalyst for both solo scenarios.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/jSnbiEyZG8K8jeagS3eZM.webp\" style=\"width: 320px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 158, 217);\">☆</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> You know Eli from your late teens/early 20's. </span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 158, 217);\">☆</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> You and Eli have never hooked up before but there has always been <em>something there</em></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 158, 217);\">☆</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Elijah was part of a band called Night Wolves, he left the band three years ago to enter rehab for his heroin addiction. He has been sober for two years. </span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 158, 217);\">☆</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Elijah now owns his grandfather's historic mechanic shop and works on solo music in his spare time.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/DOQfSHAMzVTmnmfumEEh-.webp\" style=\"width: 237px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fko-fi.com%2Fm00nprincess%2Fcommissions\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">♥</span><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 207, 240);\"><strong>Commissions on KoFi</strong></span></a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fko-fi.com%2Fm00nprincess%2Fcommissions\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">♥</span></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FUBwqnaGZstzJAGZk8\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 207, 240);\"><strong>Bot Request Form</strong></span></a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fko-fi.com%2Fm00nprincess%2Fcommissions\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"col